Background

		Mr. David L. Sokol serves as the Chief Executive Officer and Chairman of Teton Capital Group, LLC. Mr. Sokol served as an Interim Chief Executive Officer of NetJets, Inc. from August 2009 to March 30, 2011. He served as the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of NetJets, Inc. from August 2009 to March 30, 2011 and since 2009 respectively. Mr. Sokol served as the Chief Executive Officer of MidAmerican Energy Holdings Company (now Berkshire Hathaway Energy ... Company) from April 19, 1993 to April 16, 2008 and served as its President from April 19, 1993 to January 21, 1995. Formerly, among other positions held in the independent power industry, Mr. Sokol served as President and Chief Executive Officer of Kiewit Energy Company and Ogden Projects Inc. Mr. Sokol served as the Chief Executive Officer and Chairman of the Board of Managers of MidAmerican Funding LLC since its formation in March 1999. He served as a Manager of Berkshire. He serves as Chairman of Omaha Metropolitan Entertainment and Convention Authority. Mr. Sokol served as the Chairman of the Board of Ce Casecnan Water & Energy Co., Inc. He served as the Chairman of HomeServices of America, Inc. since inception in July 1999. He served as the Chairman of the Board of MidAmerican Energy Holdings Company since May 1994 until April 21, 2011. He served as Chairman of Northern Electric PLC. He served as the Chairman Emeritus of the Horatio Alger Association. He has been a Director of Seaspan Corporation since April 10, 2017 and HomeServices of America, Inc. since July 1999. He serves as a Director of WashCo. He serves as a Director of Omaha Nebraska Airport Authority (formerly Omaha Airport Authority). He served as Director of MidAmerican Energy Holdings since March 1991 until April 21, 2011. He served as a Director of Ce Casecnan Water & Energy Co., Inc. He served as a Director of MidAmerican Funding LLC, since formation in March 1999. He served as Non-executive Director of BYD Company Ltd. from August 4, 2009 to April 1, 2011. He served as a Director of NetJets Inc. from August 2009 to March 30, 2011. He served as a Director of Northern Electric PLC and Northern Powergrid Holdings Company from January 1997 to June 1, 2007. He also served as a Director of CE Electric UK Funding Company until June 1, 2007. He holds a Bachelor of Science in Civil Engineering from University of Nebraska, Omaha in 1978 and Honorary Doctorate from Bellevue University Bellevue Nebrask.Read Full Background




