This article contains content that is written like a promotional version of the subject's life, especially in the Early life and Professional career sections. Please help improve it by removing promotional content and inappropriate external links, and by adding encyclopedic content written from a neutral point of view. (August 2015) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)




David L. Sokol



Dave Sokol at the Berkshire Hathaway annual meeting



Born
David L. Sokol
